e%20empire%20there%20is%20no%20arguing%20that%20he%20is%20now%20very%20rich.%20The%20net%20worth%20of%20the%20president-elect%20sits%20at%20%245.6%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes'%20estimates%20as%20of%20Thursday%2C%20November%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Trump%20prepares%20for%20a%20second%20term%20as%20president%2C%20it%20looks%20as%20if%20like%20attracts%20like%3A%20He%20counts%20several%20billionaires%20among%20his%20advisors%20and%20cabinet%20nominees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20first-term%20cabinet%20was%20the%20wealthiest%20in%20modern%20times%20and%20included%20several%20multimillionaires%20among%20its%20ranks%2C%20including%20centimillionaires%20Wilbur%20Ross%20and%20Steve%20Mnuchin.%20Betsy%20DeVos%2C%20his%20former%20Secretary%20of%20Education%2C%20and%20her%20family%20were%20worth%20%242%20billion%20when%20she%20held%20office%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fchasewithorn%2F2019%2F07%2F24%2Finside-betsy-devos-billions-just-how-rich-is-the-education-secretary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20More%20billionaires%2C%20including%20Diane%20Hendricks%20and%20Isaac%20Perlmutter%2C%20were%20among%20his%20early%20advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20more%20clarity%20about%20the%20net%20worths%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-cabinet-deferred-capital-gains-tax-divest-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20current%20cabinet%20picks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20remaining%20nominees%20when%20they%20file%20public%20financial%20disclosures%20due%20soon%20after%20their%20nominations%20become%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20disclosures%20will%20also%20bring%20to%20light%20any%20conflicts%20of%20interest%2C%20which%20often%20result%20in%20large%20divestments.%20For%20example%2C%20in%202017%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-treasury-nominee-mnuchin-pledges-to-divest-assets-worth-at-least-94-million-2