20the%20High%20Court%20has%20an%20opportunity%20to%20hear%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeace%20and%20harmony%20must%20be%20ensured.%20We%20will%20keep%20this%20pending.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20anything%20to%20happen.%20We%20have%20to%20be%20absolutely%20neutral%20and%20ensure%20that%20nothing%20untoward%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjiv%20Khanna.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20to%20hear%20the%20plea%20filed%20by%20the%20mosque%20management%20committee%20within%20three%20working%20days%20of%20submission.%20The%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20trial%20court%20hearing%20scheduled%20for%20January%208%20would%20not%20proceed%20until%20the%20High%20Court%20has%20reviewed%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EViolent%20Clashes%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaos%20erupted%20in%20Sambhal%20earlier%20this%20week%20as%20the%20court-ordered%20survey%20of%20the%20mosque%20led%20to%20violent%20clashes%20between%20the%20locals%20and%20the%20police%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20several%20individuals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%2C%20police%20said%2C%20started%20when%20a%20crowd%20gathered%20near%20the%20mosque%20as%20the%20survey%20team%2C%20led%20by%20an%20%26quot%3BAdvocate%20Commissioner%2C%26quot%3B%20began%20its%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsambhal-mosque-jama-masjid-up-violence-16th-century-mosque-a-city-on-fire-sambhal-violence-explained-7100779%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E16th%20Century%20Mosque%2C%20A%20City%20On%20Fire%3A%20Sambhal%20Violence%20Explained%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20swelled%20to%20nearly%20a%20thousand%20people%2C%20and%20they%20tried%20to%20prevent%20the%20police%20from%20entering%20the%20mosque.%20Some%20people%20in%20the%20crowd%20threw%20stones%20at%20the%20police%20personnel%20stationed%20at%20the%20site.%20The%20mob%20also%20set%20ablaze%20more%20than%20ten%20vehicles.%C2%A0The%20police%20responded%20with%20tear%20gas.%20In%20the%20chaos%2C%20several%20were%20killed%20and%20over%2030%20police%20personnel%20were%20injured.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20violence%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20announced%20a%20three-member%20judicial%20inquiry%20commission%20to%20investigate%20the%20riots.%20The%20commission%20has%20been%20directed%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20within%20two%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20in%20Sambhal%20was%20heightened%20today%20as%20well%20in%20light%20of%20Friday%20prayers%20and%20the%20submission%20of%20the%20ASI%20survey%20report%20to%20the%20trial%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20MP%20from%20Sambhal%2C%20Zia%20Ur%20Rahman%20Barq%2C%20welcomed%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20crucial%20step%20toward%20restoring%20peace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20happy%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20taken%20this%20decision.%20We%20will%20soon%20file%20a%20new%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20demanding%20that%20the%20Sambhal%20incident%20be%20investigated%20by%20a%20commission%20headed%20by%20a%20sitting%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20We%20will%20very%20soon%20file%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Barq%2C%20who%20is%20among%20400%20others%20charged%20over%20the%20violence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBone%20Of%20Contention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20when%20a%20petition%20was%20filed%20in%20Sambhal%20by%20advocate%20Vishnu%20Shanker%20Jain%20and%20others.%20Mr%20Jain%2C%20also%20known%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20and%20Krishna%20Janmabhoomi%20disputes%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20was%20built%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20a%20temple%20dedicated%20to%20Lord%20Kalki.%20The%20petition%20alleged%20that%20the%20mosque%20was%20constructed%20after%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20temple%20during%20Babur's%20invasion%20in%201526-27.%20The%20petitioners%20argue%20that%20historical%20texts%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BBaburnamah%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAin-e-Akbari%26quot%3B%20document%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20temple%20by%20Babur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20claims%20that%20the%20temple%20was%20built%20by%20the%20Hindu%20mythological%20figure%20Vishwakarma%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20universe.%20Babur's%20forces%20allegedly%20destroyed%20the%20temple%20partially%20and%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20mosque%20to%20establish%20Islamic%20supremacy.%20The%20petition%20further%20criticises%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%20for%20failing%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20site%2C%20as%20it%20is%20a%20protected%20monument%20under%20the%20Ancient%20Monuments%20and%20Archaeological%20Sites%20and%20Remains%20Act%2C%201958.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20demand%20unrestricted%20access%20to%20the%20mosque%20for%20Hindus%2C%20claiming%20their%20right%20to%20worship%20was%20being%20unlawfully%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20petition%2C%20the%20court%20ordered%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20mosque%20on%20November%2019%2C%202024.%20Advocate%20Commissioner%20Ramesh%20Raghav%2C%20along%20with%20the%20district%20administration%20and%20police%2C%20carried%20out%20the%20survey%20the%20same%20day.%20This%20rapid%20action%20drew%20criticism%20from%20several%20quarters%2C%20with%20claims%20of%20judicial%20overreach%20and%20procedural%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20community%2C%20including%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20management%20committee%2C%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20survey.%20They%20pointed%20to%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%2C%201991%2C%20which%20prohibits%20altering%20the%20status%20of%20any%20religious%20site%20as%20it%20existed%20on%20August%2015%2C