20Show%20Two%20Ancient%20Human%20Ancestors%20%26quot%3BCrossed%20Paths%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAbout%201.5%20million%20years%20ago%2C%20individuals%20of%20two%20different%20species%20in%20the%20human%20evolutionary%20lineage%20trudged%20on%20a%20muddy%20lakeshore%20in%20northern%20Kenya%2C%20leaving%20behind%20intersecting%20trackways%20alongside%20the%20footprints%20of%20antelopes%2C%20horses%2C%20warthogs%2C%20giant%20storks%20and%20other%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20tracks%20turned%20into%20fossils%20that%20scientists%20have%20now%20discovered%20at%20a%20location%20called%20Koobi%20Fora%2C%20providing%20the%20first%20evidence%20that%20these%20two%20species%20-%20Paranthropus%20boisei%20and%20Homo%20erectus%20-%20shared%20the%20same%20landscape%2C%20literally%20crossing%20paths.%20The%20discovery%20raises%20intriguing%20questions%20about%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20two%20species%20and%20any%20competition%20for%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParanthropus%20boisei%2C%20the%20more%20distantly%20related%20to%20modern%20humans%20of%20the%20two%2C%20lived%20from%20about%202.3%20to%201.2%20million%20years%20ago%2C%20standing%20up%20to%20about%204%20feet%206%20inches%20(137%20cm)%20tall.%20They%20had%20a%20skull%20adapted%20for%20large%20chewing%20muscles%2C%20including%20a%20cranial%20crest%20like%20those%20in%20male%20gorillas%2C%20as%20well%20as%20massive%20molars.%20Their%20feet%20bore%20ape-like%20traits%20including%20in%20the%20big%20toe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHomo%20erectus%2C%20an%20early%20member%20of%20our%20evolutionary%20line%20with%20body%20proportions%20like%20those%20of%20Homo%20sapiens%2C%20lived%20from%20about%201.89%20million%20to%20110%2C000%20years%20ago%2C%20ranging%20from%20about%204%20feet%209%20inches%20to%206%20feet%201%20inch%20(145-185%20cm)%20tall.%20They%20had%20large%20brow%20ridges%20and%20bigger%20brains%20than%20Paranthropus%20boisei%2C%20though%20smaller%20than%20our%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20found%20the%20footprints%20in%202021%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20Lake%20Turkana.%20They%20identified%20one%20long%20trackway%20of%2012%20footprints%2C%20each%20about%2010.25%20inches%20(26%20cm)%20long%2C%20attributed%20to%20an%20adult%20Paranthropus%20boisei%20individual%20based%20on%20their%20shape%20and%20the%20manner%20of%20locomotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20isolated%20footprints%2C%20ranging%20from%208-9.25%20inches%20(20.5-23.5%20cm)%20long%20and%20resembling%20those%20of%20modern%20people%2C%20were%20almost%20perpendicular%20to%20the%20main%20trackway.%20Two%20were%20complete%20enough%20to%20attribute%20to%20Homo%20erectus%2C%20possibly%20a%20juvenile.%20The%20third%20was%20harder%20to%20assign%20confidently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20said%20the%20trackways%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20left%20within%20hours%20or%20perhaps%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20-%20the%20mud%20had%20never%20dried%20and%20cracked%20-%20and%20the%20individuals%20even%20may%20have%20seen%20each%20other.%20There%20was%20no%20evidence%20of%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fossil%20footprints%20provide%20us%20a%20clear%20picture%20of%20that%20instant%20in%20time%2C%201.5%20million%20years%20ago.%20The%20different%20human%20ancestors%20may%20well%20have%20passed%20by%20each%20other%2C%20wading%20in%20the%20shallow%20water%2C%20possibly%20hunting%20and%20gathering%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20paleoanthropologist%20Louise%20Leakey%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Koobi%20Fora%20Research%20Project%20and%20co-author%20of%20the%20study%20published%20on%20Thursday%20in%20the%20journal%20Science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20reanalyzed%20trackways%20that%20were%20previously%20discovered%20nearby%2C%20determining%20that%20both%20species%20were%20present%20together%20on%20fossilized%20muddy%20surfaces%20over%20a%20period%20spanning%20roughly%20200%2C000%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20possible%20that%20they%20competed%20directly%2C%20but%20also%20possible%20that%20they%20were%20not%20in%20direct%20competition%20and%20both%20had%20access%20to%20the%20resources%20that%20they%20needed%20on%20this%20shared%20landscape%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20paleoanthropologist%20and%20study%20lead%20author%20Kevin%20Hatala%20of%20Chatham%20University%20in%20Pittsburgh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDietary%20differences%20may%20have%20mitigated%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParanthropus%20boisei%20consumed%20low-quality%20forage%20that%20likely%20required%20repetitive%20chewing.%20Homo%20erectus%20was%20likely%20to%20be%20omnivorous%2C%20using%20tools%20to%20butcher%20carcasses%2C%20and%20also%20had%20meat%20in%20its%20diet%2C%26quot%3B%20Leakey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20human%20and%20chimpanzee%20evolutionary%20lineages%20split%20roughly%207%20million%20years%20ago%20in%20Africa.%20Species%20in%20the%20human%20lineage%20are%20called%20hominins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFootprints%20provide%20information%20on%20anatomy%2C%20locomotion%2C%20behavior%20and%20environments%20that%20skeletal%20fossils%20or%20stone%20tools%20cannot.%20The%20feet%20of%20these%20two%20species%20were%20anatomically%20distinct%2C%20and%20they%20had%20different%20gaits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tracks%20we%20attribute%20to%20Homo%20erectus%20have%20a%20very%20modern%20human-like%20shape%20with%20a%20tall%20arch%20of%20sediment%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20track%20that%20indicates%20a%20stiff%20foot%20and%20a%20walking%20gait%20that%20includes%20pushing%20off%20of%20the%20toes%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Harvard%20University%20evolutionary%20biologist%20and%20study%20co-author%20Neil%20Roach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Paranthropus%20tracks%20lack%20this%20tall%20arch%20and%20indicate%20a%20more%20flat-footed%20walk.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20Paranthropus%20tracks%20show%20a%20big%20toe%20that%20is%20a%20bit%20more%20diverged%20from%20the%20other%20toes%20and%20more%20mobile.%20Both%20of%20these%20aspects%20are%20more%20similar%20to%20the%20way%20a%20chimpanzee%20walks%2C%20although%20clearly%20distinct%20and%20intermediate%20between%20chimpanzee%20and%20human%20footprints%2C%26quot%3B%20Roach%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParanthropus%20boisei%20disappeared%20a%20few%20hundred%20thousand%20years%20after%20these%20footprints%2C%20while%20Homo%20erectus%20flourished.%20Possibly%20a%20direct%20ancestor%20of%20Homo%20sapiens%2C%20Homo%20erectus%20was%20the%20first%20human%20species%20to%20spread%20beyond%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fossil%20site%20was%20a%20resource-rich%20lakeshore%20near%20the%20mouth%20of%20a%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20we%20consistently%20see%20two%20species%20of%20hominins%20in%20these%20landscapes%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20dangerous%20animals%20such%20as%20hippos%20and%20crocodiles%2C%20suggests%20that%20these%20environments%20were%20important%20enough%20to%20our%20ancestors%20to%20be%20worth%20the%20risk%20of%20visiting%2C%26quot%3B%20Roach%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732857540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fr111f5pg_fossil-footprints_625x300_29_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffossil-footprints-show-two-ancient-human-ancestors-crossed-paths-7131299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22About%201.5%20million%20years%20ago%2C%20individuals%20of%20two%20different%20species%20in%20the%20human%20evolutionary%20lineage%20trudged%20on%20a%20muddy%20lakeshore%20in%20northern%20Kenya.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffossil-footprints-show-two-ancient-human-ancestors-crossed-paths-7131299%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Court%20summons%20Minister%20in%20Nagarjuna%20defamation%20suit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732857335000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115793216%2Cimgsize-796544.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fcourt-summons-telangana-minister-konda-surekha-over-defamation-suit-filed-by-nagarjuna%2Farticleshow%2F115793187.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115793187.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETelangana%20Minister%20Konda%20Surekha%20has%20been%20summoned%20to%20appear%20in%20a%20Hyderabad%20court%20on%20December%2012%20following%20a%20defamation%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20actor%20Nagarjuna.%20The%20complaint%20stems%20from%20Surekha%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20remarks%20linking%20Naga%20Chaitanya%20and%20Samantha%20Ruth%20Prabhu%E2%80%99s%20divorce%20to%20political%20figures.%20Despite%20retracting%20her%20statements%2C%20Surekha's%20comments%20sparked%20outrage%2C%20leading%20to%20legal%20action%20by%20Nagarjuna%2C%20with%20the%20summons%20coming%20days%20before%20Chaitanya%E2%80%99s%20wedding%20to%20Sobhita%20Dhulipala.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fcourt-summons-telangana-minister-konda-surekha-over-defamation-suit-filed-by-nagarjuna%2Farticleshow%2F115793187.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Candace%20Owens%2C%20Conservative%20Commentator%20Barred%20From%20New%20Zealand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20conservative%20political%20commentator%20Candace%20Owens%20has%20been%20denied%20entry%20to%20New%20Zealand%20for%20a%20scheduled%20speaking%20engagement%2C%20with%20immigration%20officials%20citing%20her%20ban%20from%20another%20country%20as%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20decision.%20This%20follows%20Australia's%20recent%20rejection%20of%20her%20visa%20application%20over%20controversial%20comments.%20Known%20for%20her%20provocative%20commentary%20and%20inflammatory%20takes%20on%20social%20and%20political%20issues%2C%20Owens%20has%20built%20a%20significant%20following%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20over%20three%20million%20followers%20on%20YouTube.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Early%20life%20and%20influences%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fnews%2Fannals-of-communications%2Fthe-gospel-of-candace-owens%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20Yorker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Candace%20Owens%20described%20her%20early%20years%2C%20spent%20in%20low-income%20housing%20in%20Stamford%2C%20Connecticut%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdysfunctional.%E2%80%9D%20At%20nine%2C%20her%20family%20moved%20in%20with%20her%20grandparents%2C%20where%20her%20grandfather%2C%20Robert%20Owens%2C%20became%20a%20guiding%20force%20in%20her%20life.%20Raised%20as%20one%20of%2012%20children%20on%20a%20sharecropping%20farm%20in%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Robert%20worked%20from%20the%20age%20of%20five%2C%20drying%20tobacco%20leaves%20and%20frequently%20shared%20stories%20of%20growing%20up%20Black%20in%20the%20Deep%20South%2C%20including%20harrowing%20encounters%20with%20the%20Ku%20Klux%20Klan.%20Owens%20has%20cited%20these%20family%20experiences%20to%20question%20liberal%20narratives%20about%20white%20nationalism%20in%20modern%20America.%20In%20a%202019%20Judiciary%20Committee%20hearing%20on%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20spread%20of%20white%20identity%20ideology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20criticised%20Democrats%20for%20%E2%80%9Cfear-mongering%E2%80%9D%20about%20racism%2C%20pointing%20to%20her%20grandfather's%20experiences%20under%20Democratic-led%20Jim%20Crow%20laws%20as%20evidence%20of%20the%20shifting%20political%20landscape%20of%20racial%20issues.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECandace%20Owens%2C%20a%20right-wing%20political%20commentator%2C%20has%20drawn%20attention%20for%20her%20controversial%20views%2C%20including%20the%20promotion%20of%20antisemitic%20tropes%20and%20anti-Israel%20rhetoric.%20She%20has%20also%20propagated%20conspiracy%20theories%20targeting%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community.%20Owens%20rose%20to%20prominence%20between%202016%20and%202017%20as%20a%20vocal%20supporter%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%20MAGA%20movement%20and%20a%20critic%20of%20the%20Black%20Lives%20Matter%20campaign.%20Her%20career%20saw%20significant%20growth%20during%20her%20time%20with%20Turning%20Point%20USA%20and%20later%20with%20the%20conservative%20media%20platform%2C%20The%20Daily%20Wire%2C%20co-founded%20by%20Ben%20Shapiro.%20But%20her%20tenure%20at%20The%20Daily%20Wire%20ended%20after%20increasing%20tensions%20with%20its%20founders%20over%20her%20remarks%20about%20Jews%20and%20her%20opposition%20to%20US%20military%20support%20for%20Israel.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E3)%20Recent%20controversies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECandace%20Owens%20announced%20a%20speaking%20tour%20in%20August%2C%202024%2C%20promising%20audiences%20in%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20discussions%20on%20free%20speech%20and%20her%20Christian%20beliefs.%20But%20Australia%20banned%20her%20in%20October%2C%20with%20Immigration%20Minister%20Tony%20Burke%20stating%20that%20Owens%20%E2%80%9Chas%20the%20capacity%20to%20incite%20discord%20in%20almost%20every%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20citing%20her%20controversial%20remarks%20about%20the%20Holocaust%20and%20Muslims.%20In%20New%20Zealand%2C%20officials%20denied%20her%20an%20entertainer's%20work%20permit%20based%20on%20a%20legal%20provision%20barring%20visas%20for%20individuals%20already%20excluded%20from%20another%20country.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Connection%20with%20Kanye%20West%20and%20launch%20of%20%E2%80%98Blexit'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCandace%20Owens%20gained%20further%20visibility%20when%20Kanye%20West%20(known%20as%20Ye)%20once%20publicly%20endorsed%20her%20on%20X%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20love%20the%20way%20Candace%20Owens%20thinks.%E2%80%9D%20Following%20this%2C%20Owens%20joined%20West%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20TMZ%20offices%2C%20where%20he%20made%20controversial%20comments%20about%20slavery%20being%20a%20%E2%80%9Cchoice%E2%80%9D%20for%20Black%20people.%20Building%20on%20the%20momentum%2C%20Owens%20launched%20the%20%E2%80%9CBlexit%E2%80%9D%20movement%2C%20short%20for%20%E2%80%9CBlack%20exit%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20encourages%20Black%20Americans%20to%20leave%20what%20she%20describes%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CDemocrat%20plantation.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E5)%20Personal%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCandace%20Owens%20is%20married%20to%20British%20businessman%20George%20Farmer%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Lord%20Michael%20Farmer%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20trading%20conglomerate%20Metal%20%26amp%3B%20Commodity%20Company%20Ltd.%20The%20couple%20met%20in%202018%20and%20Farmer%20proposed%20to%20her%20just%2017%20days%20after%20their%20first%20meeting%20during%20a%20FaceTime%20call%20on%20December%2029%2C%202018%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fwho-is-george-farmer-candace-owens-husband-8386561%5C%22%3EPeople%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20married%20in%202019%20and%20have%20since%20welcomed%20three%20children%20into%20their%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732856460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fee7kb3a8_candace-owens-instagram_625x300_29_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-candace-owens-conservative-commentator-barred-from-new-zealand-7131063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20conservative%20political%20commentator%20Candace%20Owens%20has%20been%20denied%20entry%20to%20New%20Zea