e%20people%20to%20use%20them.%20They%20also%20have%20schemes%20like%20the%20%E2%80%98T%20Verda%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20which%20offers%20a%20three-year%20free%20transit%20pass%20to%20people%20who%20scrap%20old%2C%20polluting%20vehicles%20and%20commit%20to%20not%20purchasing%20another%20%E2%80%94%20directly%20addressing%20emissions%20from%20private%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20air%20quality%20improves%20in%20the%20city%2C%20Barcelona%20is%20observing%20socio-economic%20benefits.%20There%20has%20been%20a%2030%25%20rise%20in%20commercial%20activity%2C%20especially%20in%20areas%20with%20reduced%20vehicle%20traffic%20and%20more%20pedestrian-friendly%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExpanding%20green%20spaces%20for%20cleaner%20air%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarcelona%20has%20also%20focused%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328522%2Fhow-nature-based-solutions-can-help-build-climate-change-resilience-wri-projects%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eurban%20greening%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20goal%20of%20increasing%20its%20green%20spaces.%20They%20plan%20on%20adding%20more%20than%20160%20hectares%20of%20green%20space%20by%202030%2C%20which%20will%20help%20improve%20air%20quality%2C%20absorb%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20and%20manage%20the%20urban%20heat%20island%20effect.%20Green%20spaces%20like%20parks%2C%20gardens%2C%20and%20tree-lined%20streets%20provide%20a%20natural%20buffer%20to%20pollution.%20The%20%E2%80%9CTrees%20for%20Living%E2%80%9D%20initiative%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Barcelona%20Tree%20Master%20Plan%2C%20aims%20to%20increase%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20tree%20cover%20and%20better%20its%20natural%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Jha%20aptly%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndeed%2C%20it%20%5Bair%20pollution%5D%20is%20no%20more%20just%20an%20environmental%20crisis%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20public%20health%20crisis.%20There%20is%20enough%20empirical%20data%20and%20research%20that%20talks%20about%20the%20grave%20public%20health%20impact%20it%20has.%20We%20cannot%20fix%20the%20problem%20through%20individual%20efforts%20like%20air%20purifiers%20or%20the%20luxury%20of%20leaving%20the%20city.%20We%20need%20a%20collective%20solution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Endolla%20Barcelona%2C%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20electromobility%20network%2C%20the%20use%20of%20EVs%20prevented%20the%20emission%20of%208%2C989%20tons%20of%20CO2%20in%202023.%20Barcelona%20is%20leading%20the%20way%20in%20sustainable%20urban%20development%20with%20improved%20air%20quality.%20The%20city%20sets%20a%20global%20benchmark%20for%20cleaner%20cities%20and%20shows%20how%20sustainable%20urban%20planning%20can%20simultaneously%20improve%20public%20health%2C%20economic%20vitality%2C%20and%20environmental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fd%2Fd5%2FN1529189.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETransforming%20our%20world%3A%20the%202030%20Agenda%20for%20Sustainable%20Development%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3A%20by%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%2C%20Published%20on%2021%20October%202015.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732854590000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D384037%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Learn%20how%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20innovative%20urban%20planning%2C%20green%20initiatives%2C%20and%20public%20transport%20reforms%20offer%20actionable%20solutions%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20growing%20air%20pollution%20crisis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebette