Experts%20say%20drinking%20raw%20milk%20is%20dangerous%2C%20and%20can%20cause%20food%20poisoning.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20batch%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-raw-unpasteurized-milk-healthy-safe-to-drink-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraw%20milk%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20tested%20positive%20for%20bird%20flu%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20Sunday%2C%20Fresno-based%20Raw%20Farm%20voluntarily%20recalled%20a%20first%20batch%20of%20cream%20top%20whole%20raw%20milk%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bbest%20by%26quot%3B%20date%20of%20November%2027.%20By%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20California%20Department%20of%20Public%20Health%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdph.ca.gov%2FPrograms%2FOPA%2FPages%2FNR24-042.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20second%20batch%20of%20Raw%20Farm%20cream%20top%2C%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bbest%20by%26quot%3B%20date%20of%20December%207%20had%20also%20tested%20positive%20for%20bird%20flu%2C%20based%20on%20retail%20sampling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20making%20a%20big%20deal%20about%20it%2C%20because%20it's%20not%20a%20big%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaleigh%20Stanziani%2C%20Raw%20Farm's%20vice%20president%20of%20marketing%2C%20said%20in%20a%20short%20video%20posted%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshorts%2Fo6COUza-wLU%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20farm's%20first%20voluntary%20recall%20was%20announced%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20there%20had%20only%20been%20an%20indication%20that%20there%20might%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Btrace%20element%20of%20something%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20emphasizing%20that%20there%20had%20been%20no%20reported%20illnesses%20of%20Raw%20Farms%20cows%20or%20positive%20tests%20from%20the%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaw%20Farm%20owner%20Mark%20McAfee%20later%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fenvironment%2Fstory%2F2024-11-27%2Fcalifornia-recalls-more-raw-milk-after-bird-flu-test-results%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAccording%2520to%2520Mark%2520McAfee%252C%2520the%2Cof%2520further%2520products%25E2%2580%259D%2520until%2520Friday.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELA%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20California%20Department%20of%20Food%20and%20Agriculture%20had%20requested%20that%20his%20company%20%26quot%3Bhold%20delivery%20of%20further%20products%26quot%3B%20until%20Friday%2C%20after%20conducting%20thorough%20testing%20of%20two%20Raw%20Farms%20and%20one%20creamery%20on%20Wednesday.%20(McAfee%20could%20not%20immediately%20be%20reached%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider%20during%20the%20Thanksgiving%20holiday.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f72d2837-697f-4c2b-b992-1d3b883794bf%5C%22%3ERaw%20milk%20may%20be%20helping%20bird%20flu%20spread%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20in%20the%20way%20you%20might%20think%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22raw%20milk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6748ef23ede4eeae392a45af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222689%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EContainers%20of%20Raw%20Farm%20raw%20milk%20on%20a%20shelf%20at%20Berkeley%20Bowl%20on%20November%2025%2C%202024%20in%20Berkeley%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D3993a6d177fa329f2ab85fce6f69866ed7d9d616a2363a6d35cc591a481fbca3%26postID%3D6748cf9fd282deffb9ce4ea7%26postSlug%3Draw-farm-milk-california-tests-positive-bird-flu-2024-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fd41586-024-01624-1%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuspect%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20cross-contamination%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbird-flu-cows-milk-spread-study-suggests-how-to-stop-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraw%20milk%20between%20animals%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20one%20reason%20the%20H5N1%20virus%20is%20spreading%20rapidly%20among%20cows%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20and%20could%20even%20contribute%20to%20the%20human%20spread%20of%20the%20virus.%20The%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20cautions%20that%20dairy%20workers%20might%20be%20able%20to%20contract%20bird%20flu%20by%20infected%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdph.ca.gov%2FPrograms%2FCID%2FDCDC%2Fpages%2FBird-Flu.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraw%20milk%20splashed%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20their%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20definitive%20evidence%20yet%20that%20humans%20can%20get%20bird%20flu%20from%20drinking%20contaminated%20raw%20milk.%20Instead%2C%20health%20authorities%20generally%20recommend%20avoiding%20raw%20milk%20because%20of%20other%20serious%20health%20risks%2C%20including%20food%20poisoning%20with%20bacteria%20like%20Salmonella%2C%20E.coli%2C%20or%20Listeria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20known%20health%20benefits%20of%20drinking%20raw%20milk.%20Instead%2C%20all%20evidence%20suggests%20that%20pasteurized%20milk%20is%20just%20as%20nutritious%2C%20and%20is%20safer%20to%20consume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20raw%20milk%20has%20become%20a%20trendy%20product%20among%20some%20influencers.%20Gwenyth%20Paltrow%20says%20she%20has%20it%20in%20her%20coffee%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-rfk-jr-plans-to-make-america-healthy-again-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20President-elect%20Trump's%20pick%20for%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%20secretary%2C%20says%20he%20wants%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20to%20stop%20its%20%26quot%3Bwar%26quot%3B%20against%20raw%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20summer%2C%20%26quot%3BCarnivore%20MD%26quot%3B%20Paul%20Saladino%20released%20a%20raw%20milk%20smoothie%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20elite%20Los%20Angeles%20health%20foods%20store%20Erewhon%20featuring%20unpasteurized%20(raw)%20kefir%20from%20Raw%20Farms%2C%20and%20powdered%20beef%20organs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20has%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fphlp%2Fphp%2Fpublications%2Funpasteurized-cow-milk.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloosest%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20raw%20milk%20in%20the%20country%3B%20it's%20generally%20fine%20for%20California%20retailers%20like%20health%20foods%20stores%20and%20grocers%20to%20sell%20it%2C%20raw%20milk%20products%20just%20can't%20be%20transported%20across%20state%20lines%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ffood%2Fbuy-store-serve-safe-food%2Ffood-safety-and-raw-milk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFDA%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225082%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22raw%20milk%20smoothie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6748eec19f2901eb60379363%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%227619%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Paul's%20Raw%20Animal-Based%20Smoothie%20includes%20Raw%20Farm%20kefir%20milk%2C%20beef%20organ%20powder%2C%20as%20well%20as%20blueberries%2C%20honey%2C%20bananas%20and%20other%20ingredients.%20It's%20%2419.%3Cp%3EDania%20Maxwell%2FLos%20Angeles%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Payne%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20the%20Western%20Institute%20of%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Security%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffood%2Farticle%2F2024%2Fjun%2F09%2Fraw-milk-powdered-meat-smoothie-erewhon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20people%20consuming%20Dr.%20Paul's%20%2419%20smoothie%20were%20%26quot%3Bplaying%20Russian%20roulette%20with%20their%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20ignoring%20pasteurization%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20single%20most%20important%20food%20safety%20firewall%20in%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20dairy%20farms%20have%20been%20seeing%20an%20uptick%20in%20bird%20flu%20cases%20since%20August.%20The%20state%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdph.ca.gov%2FPrograms%2FCID%2FDCDC%2Fpages%2FBird-Flu.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2029%20confirmed%20human%20cases%20of%20bird%20flu%2C%20and%20all%20but%20one%20of%20those%20was%20sourced%20back%20to%20cows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20reported%20the%20first%20confirmed%20case%20of%20bird%20flu%20in%20a%20California%20child%20from%20Alameda%20County.%20The%20child%20had%20no%20known%20contact%20with%20infected%20farm%20animals%2C%20but%20may%20have%20been%20exposed%20to%20wild%20birds%2C%20the%20California%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdph.ca.gov%2FPrograms%2FOPA%2FPages%2FNR24-037.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealth%20department%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20child%20had%20mild%20symptoms%20and%20is%20recovering%20well%20after%20receiving%20antiviral%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraw-farm-milk-california-tests-positive-bird-flu-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732838271000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6748e5ccfa0140cdd5661f5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraw-farm-milk-california-tests-positive-bird-flu-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20second%20batch%20of%20cream%20top%20whole%20raw%20milk%20from%20Raw%20Farm%20in%20California%20just%20tested%20positive%20for%20bird%20flu.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbrueck%40businessinsider.com%20(Hilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider