s%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20caught%20and%20worked%20through%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rishabh%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERoping%20in%20%3Cem%3EKabadi%20wallas%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20new%20vision%2C%20Rishabh%20dialled%20Nitin.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20and%20I%20have%20always%20had%20complimentary%20qualities.%20So%2C%20I%20told%20him%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20something%2C%20and%20he%20was%20immediately%20on%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rishabh.%20The%20two%20soon%20became%20partners%20in%20a%20venture%20that%20would%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20skill%20and%20passion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20around%20just%20looking%20at%20dumpyards%20and%20the%20heaps%20of%20trash%20that%20was%20piled%20up%20there%2C%20either%20waiting%20to%20be%20burnt%20or%20to%20end%20up%20in%20a%20landfill%20for%20life%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289075%2Fisb-grad-helps-large-fmcg-brands-recycle-plastic-packaging-reduce-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20was%20the%20biggest%20culprit%3C%2Fa%3E%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Nitin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20months%20of%20research%2C%20compliance%20checks%2C%20and%20operational%20planning%2C%20the%20two%20friends%20registered%20their%20company%2C%20%E2%80%98Dump%20In%20Bin%E2%80%99.%20However%2C%20tapping%20into%20an%20industry%20that%20is%20largely%20informal%2C%20threw%20up%20several%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20initial%20days%20of%20the%20company%2C%20Rishabh%20and%20Nitin%20focused%20on%20aggregating%20waste%20from%20small-scale%20collectors%20or%20%3Cem%3Ekabadi%20wallas%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20and%20around%20Delhi.%20These%20informal%20waste%20workers%20were%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20their%20operations%2C%20collecting%20waste%20from%20households%20and%20streets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20building%20strong%20relationships%20with%2015-20%20clusters%20of%20garbage%20collectors%2C%20%E2%80%98Dump%20In%20Bin%E2%80%99%20managed%20to%20thrive%20in%20the%20early%20stages.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20when%20we%20were%20working%20with%20some%20larger%20sellers%2C%20we%20could%20only%20break%20even.%20But%20working%20with%20these%20people%2C%20we%20were%20doing%20well%20for%20ourselves%20and%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rishabh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20they%20realised%20that%20industrial%20waste%2C%20particularly%20plastic%2C%20offered%20the%20greatest%20potential%20for%20recycling%20and%20reuse.%20But%20recycling%20plastic%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20complexity%20of%20plastic%20is%20that%20you%20cannot%20intermix%20it.%20Different%20grades%20of%20plastic%20need%20to%20be%20processed%20separately%2C%20so%20that%20the%20end%20product%20is%20actually%20useful%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rishabh%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20challenges%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20profits%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20research%2C%20and%20trial-and-error%2C%20the%20company%20chose%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20automotive%20industry%2C%20where%20high-grade%20plastic%20is%20used%20for%20manufacturing%20car%20parts.%20%E2%80%98Dump%20In%20Bin%E2%80%99%20began%20processing%20plastic%20waste%20from%20automotive%20manufacturers%2C%20refining%20their%20segregation%20process%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20plastics%20were%20sorted%20properly%20before%20being%20recycled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20a%20thorough%20and%20diligent%20process%2C%20the%20company%20built%20expertise%20in%20plastic%20recycling%2C%20particularly%20in%20turning%20plastic%20waste%20into%20usable%20raw%20materials.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20initial%20trails%20were%20maddening!%20We%20even%20built%20small%20%3Cem%3Echulas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20experimented%20with%20melting%20small%20amounts%20of%20plastic%20in%20pans%2C%20using%20different%20methods%20at%20a%20very%20small%20scale%20to%20see%20what%20works%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nitin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-19-at-3.31.54-PM-1732198155.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20'Plave%2C'%20a%20precast%20concrete%20material%20created%20from%20recycled%20demolition%20debris%20and%20plastic%20waste.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-19-at-3.31.54-PM-1732198155.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-19-at-3.31.54-PM-1732198155-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-19-at-3.31.54-PM-1732198155-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-19-at-3.31.54-PM-1732198155-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-19-at-3.31.54-PM-1732198155-1200x675.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-19-at-3.31.54-PM-1732198155-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381947%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPLAVE%20(a%20play%20on%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98pavement%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98plastic%E2%80%99)%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20help%20small%20and%20medium-sized%20manufacturing%20companies%20(SMEs)%20to%20make%20a%20more%20sustainable%20and%20cheaper%20choice%20in%20their%20production%20process.%20%E2%80%9CRecycled%20plastic%20can%20be%20used%20for%20anything%2C%20but%20we%20make%20sure%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20used%20for%20or%20around%20food%20packaging.%20Because%20it%E2%80%99s%20still%20plastic%2C%20recycled%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rishabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20focus%20on%20sustainability%20has%20paid%20off.%20%E2%80%98Dump%20In%20Bin%E2%80%99%20has%20recycled%20over%2048%20lakh%20kg%20of%20plastic%2C%20bringing%20in%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPLAVE%3A%20A%20breakthrough%20in%20sustainability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20founders%20had%20bigger%20aspirations.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20just%20another%20recycling%20company%3B%20they%20wanted%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20of%20waste%20in%20a%20more%20tangible%20and%20sustainable%20way.%20The%20idea%20of%20creating%20a%20product%20that%20could%20replace%20cement%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20carbon-intensive%20materials%20used%20in%20construction%2C%20became%20their%20next%20goal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fstories%2F2024%2F09%2Fcement-production-sustainable-concrete-co2-emissions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20global%20cement%20manufacturing%20produced%201.6%20billion%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20CO2%20in%202022%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20about%208%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20total%20CO2%20emissions%2C%20making%20it%20a%20significant%20contributor%20to%20climate%20change.%20The%20challenge%20was%20daunting%3A%20they%20needed%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20make%20a%20product%20that%20could%20replace%20cement%20but%20still%20meet%20the%20high-quality%20standards%20required%20for%20construction%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20breakthrough%20came%20when%20they%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20decade-old%20research%20project%20that%20explored%20mixing%20plastic%20with%20sand%20to%20create%20concrete.%20However%2C%20the%20research%20was%20still%20in%20its%20infancy%2C%20and%20the%20existing%20products%20didn%E2%80%99t%20match%20the%20quality%20of%20cement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20two%20years%20of%20research%20and%20development%2C%20they%20created%20PLAVE%20(a%20play%20on%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98pavement%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98plastic%E2%80%99)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20unique%20construction%20material%20made%20from%20a%20blend%20of%20plastic%20waste%20and%20demolition%20debris.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Patel%20and%20Nitin%20Yadav%20in%20their%20plastic%20recycling%20facility.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244-1200x675.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381949%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20waste%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20pile%20up%20%E2%80%94%20it%20gets%20used%2C%20it%20gets%20recycled%2C%20and%20it%20becomes%20a%20part%20of%20something%20new.%E2%80%9D-%20Rishabh%20Patel%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPLAVE%20was%20designed%20so%20that%20waste%20is%20not%20only%20consumed%20but%20transformed%20into%20a%20product%20that%20can%20be%20used%20again.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20win-win%20scenario%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rishabh.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20win%20because%20we%20make%20money%20doing%20something%20good%2C%20the%20people%20we%20work%20with%20win%20because%20they%20get%20good%20products%20at%20a%20great%20cost%2C%20and%20the%20world%20wins%20because%20the%20work%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20is%20good.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20innovative%20products%20they%20have%20developed%20using%20this%20material%20is%20permeable%20pavement%2C%20which%20allows%20water%20to%20pass%20through%20it%20and%20aids%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357468%2Fias-officer-revive-water-table-cdo-varanasi-himanshu-nagpal-rainwater-harvesting-river-rejuvenation-groundwater-recharge%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20groundwater%20recharge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20helping%20to%20keep%20roads%20dry%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECommunity%20engagement%20and%20social%20impact%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20just%20business%2C%20%E2%80%98Dump%20In%20Bin%E2%80%99%20is%20deeply%20committed%20to%20social%20impact.%20A%20chance%20encounter%20with%20Parnika%20Shrimali%2C%20a%20Gurgaon%20resident%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20dispose%20of%20household%20plastic%20waste%20is%20now%20turning%20into%20a%20partnership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20finding%20out%20about%20the%20company%2C%20Parnika%2C%20who%20had%20some%20household%20plastic%20waste%20that%20she%20needed%20to%20put%20to%20use%2C%20contacted%20Rishabh.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20to%20collect%20the%20trash%20and%20it%20was%20a%20very%20small%20amount%20compared%20to%20what%20we%20usually%20work%20with.%20But%20she%20was%20so%20passionate%20about%20not%20throwing%20away%20the%20trash%20mindlessly%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20take%20it%20off%20her%20hands%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rishabh.%20Parnika%E2%80%99s%20apartment%20complex%20is%20now%20collaborating%20with%20%E2%80%98Dump%20In%20Bin%E2%80%99%20to%20set%20up%20regular%20plastic%20waste%20collection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20and%20Nitin%20also%20wish%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20ragpickers%20%E2%80%94%20the%20unsung%20heroes%20of%20the%20waste%20management%20industry%20who%20often%20work%20in%20unsafe%2C%20hazardous%20conditions.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20spoke%20to%20them%20and%20tried%20to%20convince%20them%20that%20whatever%20you%20are%20doing%20in%20collaboration%20with%20different%20contractors%20is%20a%20different%20thing%2C%20but%20we%20would%20like%20to%20work%20with%20you%2C%20give%20you%20a%20proper%20place%20to%20live%20and%20just%20make%20the%20job%20more%20dignified%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rishabh%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PLAVE%20gaining%20traction%20and%20their%20waste%20collection%20operations%20expanding%2C%20Rishabh%20and%20Nitin%20are%20now%20working%20towards%20setting%20up%20a%20Material%20Recovery%20Facility%20(MRF)%20and%20are%20exploring%20new%20ways%20to%20reduce%20plastic%20consumption%20across%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20waste%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20pile%20up%20%E2%80%94%20it%20gets%20used%2C%20it%20gets%20recycled%2C%20and%20it%20becomes%20a%20part%20of%20something%20new%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rishabh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Dump%20In%20Bin%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732678200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-19-at-3.31.53-PM-3-1732198036.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D381912%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rishabh%20Patel%20and%20Nitin%20Yadav%20are%20turning%20the%20tide%20with%20Dump%20In%20Bin.%20By%20focusing%20on%20the%20recycling%20of%20plastic%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20created%20a%20system%20that%20not%20only%20reduces%20waste%20but%20transforms%20it%20into%20valuable%20materials%20for%20industries%2C%20helping%20businesses%20save%20costs%20while%20contributing%20to%20a%20cleaner%20environment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F381912%2Fdump-in-bin-plastic-waste-recycled-materials-plave%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Worker%20Sues%20Kroger%20And%20Albertsons%2C%20Alleging%20Collusion%20Against%20Union%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20lawsuit%20claims%20the%20supermarket%20giants%20reached%20a%20deal%20not%20to%20poach%20striking%20workers%20in%20order%20to%20reduce%20the%20union's%20negotiating%20leverage.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732643187000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F6745f7e71900002c008ffd65.jpeg%3Fops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fworker-sues-kroger-albertsons-alleging-collusion-against-union_n_6745f640e4b0fffc5a468583%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20lawsuit%20claims%20the%20supermarket%20giants%20reached%20a%20deal%20not%20to%20poach%20striking%20workers%20in%20order%20to%20reduce%20the%20union's%20negotiating%20leverage.%22%2