dia.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20at%20home%2C%20my%20father%20sang%20a%20variety%20of%20classical%20compositions%20from%20different%20composers%2C%20and%20as%20he%20tells%20it%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20form%20and%20structure%20of%20about%2040%20ragas%20(musical%20modes%20in%20Carnatic%20music)%20with%20whatever%20limited%20syllables%20I%20could%20pronounce%20at%20the%20time.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20he%20observed%20early%20on%20that%20I%20had%20a%20%E2%80%98gift%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20such%20incident%20occurred%20when%20Varijashree%20was%20four%20years%20old.%20By%20this%20age%2C%20she%20was%20already%20delivering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F192140%2Fmysore-maharaja-wadiyar-western-classical-music-history-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclassical%20Carnatic%20music%3C%2Fa%3E%20vocal%20performances%20to%20small%20audiences.%20And%20this%20particular%20incident%20took%20place%20during%20one%20of%20her%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20concept%20of%20the%20concert%20was%20that%20I%20would%20sing%20for%20an%20hour.%20Many%20musicians%20attended%20this%20concert%2C%20and%20after%20my%20hour-long%20performance%2C%20they%20sang%20a%20set%20of%20compositions%20in%20100%20different%20%3Cem%3Eragas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20had%20to%20identify%20each%20%3Cem%3Eraga%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20I%20did%20successfully.%20This%20concert%20was%20filmed%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20person%20who%20recorded%20it%20lost%20the%20VHS%20tape.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5