20are%20counted%20%E2%80%94%20one%20EVM%20per%20table.%20Once%20the%20votes%20are%20tallied%2C%20the%20results%20for%20that%20round%20are%20immediately%20displayed%20and%20recorded%20on%20a%20blackboard%20attached%20to%20each%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20system%20ensures%20complete%20transparency%20and%20allows%20representatives%20to%20verify%20the%20results%20in%20real-time.%20Subsequent%20rounds%20only%20begin%20after%20the%20results%20of%20the%20previous%20round%20are%20confirmed.%20The%20RO%20supervises%20the%20entire%20process%2C%20ensuring%20that%20it%20is%20conducted%20systematically%20and%20in%20compliance%20with%20election%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20612px)%20100vw%2C%20612px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fistockphoto-1217030212-612x612-1-1732521800.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22612%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20counting%20of%20votes%20begin%20with%20the%20counting%20of%20post%20ballots%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fistockphoto-1217030212-612x612-1-1732521800.jpg%20612w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fistockphoto-1217030212-612x612-1-1732521800-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fistockphoto-1217030212-612x612-1-1732521800-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fistockphoto-1217030212-612x612-1-1732521800-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382441%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22408%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20counting%20of%20votes%20begin%20with%20the%20counting%20of%20post%20ballots%20(This%20picture%20is%20sourced%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nor