fficial%20records.%20This%20step%20ensures%20the%20official%20compilation%20and%20validation%20of%20the%20election%20data.%20The%20ECI%20oversees%20the%20verification%20of%20all%20results%20and%20ensures%20that%20all%20records%20are%20securely%20archived%20for%20future%20reference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Sealing%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20results%20are%20declared%2C%20the%20EVMs%20and%20VVPAT%20units%20are%20resealed%20and%20stored%20securely%20at%20the%20counting%20centres.%20These%20machines%20are%20retained%20for%20potential%20future%20verification%20or%20recounting%20and%20can%20be%20inspected%20if%20necessary.%20This%20ensures%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20transparent%20recount%20process%20should%20any%20concerns%20arise%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E9.%20Official%20declaration%20of%20results%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20results%2C%20including%20the%20total%20number%20of%20votes%20each%20candidate%20has%20received%2C%20are%20officially%20declared%20by%20the%20RO.%20The%20ECI%20then%20compiles%20these%20results%20from%20all%20constituencies%20and%20announces%20them%20to%20the%20public%2C%20typically%20by%20evening%2C%20once%20the%20counting%20and%20validation%20processes%20are%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Findia-vote-election-counting-modi-1908222%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Findia-vote-election-counting-modi-1908222%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20India%20Counted%2064